      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK CHANCE (6) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at her last six on end, the latest at this track (25.55). Happy to have her on top this line-up. PELOPONNESE (8) shapes well for this on her fast win a few runs back, getting around Wagga over 525m in 30.32 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Has the ability and can find winning form again. YATHONG TIGER (3) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Elle's Moon (31.07) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than last start and can bounce back. SIZZLE JACK (7) hit the frame latest (26.01) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Has already won two times from this draw.",
